\par }{\fs20\cf0 
Each seed description hereafter describes the relevant Knowledge (arcane lore) check DC for incantations using the seed and describes typical effects that incantations with that seed produce. Most of the parameters of the seed (range, duration, 
and so on) can be modified for a specific incantation by applying factors, described in the seed description and in Table: General Factors.
\par The following seeds can be used alone or in combination to create incantations for any purpose. If you\rquote re seeking an effect not described below, simply choose a seed that approximates what you\rquote 
re looking for, then apply an ad-hoc adjustment as you see fit.}{\b\fs28\cf0 
